description:
Ukraine has launched a devastating series of covert strikes on Russia’s shadow fleet, crippling five tankers between January 28 and June 29, 2025. These attacks come as Russia’s shadow fleet has ballooned to 400–600 ships, facilitating oil exports worth over $610 billion since 2022.
